             was indicted for <rs id="t18230625-3-off16" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230625-3-off16" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-3-off16" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230625-3-cd17" type="crimeDate">20th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-3-off16 t18230625-3-cd17"></join>, at <placeName id="t18230625-3-crimeloc18">St. Mary, Islington</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-3-crimeloc18" type="placeName" value="St. Mary, Islington"></interp>
