                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-3-defend82 t18230625-3-punish23"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 16.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy, on account of his youth, by the Prosecutor and Jury.</p>
